Kigeli V w'u Rwanda (yabatijwe Jean-Baptiste Ndahindurwa (Kamembe, ku ya 29 Kamena 1936 - Washington DC, ku ya 16 Ukwakira 2016) yari umwami wa nyuma (Mwami) w'u Rwanda, kuva ku ya 28 Nyakanga 1959 kugeza kwimikwa kwayo ku ya 28 Mutarama 1961, mbere gato yuko Ububiligi butanga ubwigenge muri iki gihugu.

Igihe yari mu buhungiro muri Amerika, ntabwo yigeze yima uburenganzira bwe bw'ingoma kandi yafatwaga nk'umwami wa Jura w'u Rwanda, ayobora umusingi utanga ubufasha bw'ikiremwamuntu ku Rwanda.
